{"tid":818962,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【上海騷被維穩】歌迷遭保安拖走毆打 英國「新人王」Dua Lipa無力阻止","createTime":"2018-09-14T12:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T13:05:37.000Z","uid":13273,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8f3f3be6cdc8c9937b819e2ecbad76590645f3","tid":818962,"uid":13273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"曾於去年喺香港舉行演唱會嘅英國「新人王」歌手Dua Lipa，噚晚於中國上海開個唱，當中好多歌迷於場中企起身跳舞，點知竟被現場保安指罵、毆打、暴力拖出場外，引發歌迷及網友震怒，Dua更因無力阻止傷心落淚。<br />\n<br />\n據指噚晚有唔少歌迷都於演唱會中，企起身跟住音樂跳舞，點知就立即被數名保安上前喝令坐低，甚至有人直接被拖出場外，仲有女歌迷以為保安係上前互動，點知被保安直接抱起撻落地後拖走，又有觀眾被保安帶出場外後遭到一群保安圍攻毆打。<br />\n<br />\nDua於台上都發現情況，但似乎無力阻止，更數度哽咽表示：「我本來希望為歌迷提供一個安全嘅環境，等大家可以唱歌跳舞，仲有最後幾首歌，希望大家能夠好好享受。」又有歌迷指帶來嘅LGBT彩虹旗被保安搶走。事件除咗令樂迷震怒，外媒都紛紛報道，引起國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180913/58677473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58677473&d=wpkqGnotLFXjRJu74z6Y4jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=53317369\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58677473&h=d5d7a947\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180913/58677473</a><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5Xkx3DR_Qk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD5Xkx3DR_Qk&d=wpkqGnotLFXjRJu74z6Y4jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c69cff86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5Xkx3DR_Qk</a><br />\n<br />\nDua好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個concert都要俾啲無謂人阻住曬<br />\n不過當做個版俾其他外國歌手睇<br />\n以後咪再去中國<br />\n嚟多啲香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1942cef3ce9dc5cf0f46dd59a7bfcaad2f63f0","tid":818962,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"這就是中國特色,境外勢力及媒體不得干預中國事務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}